      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/nagaraja-compression-bending-vr-002",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "F1717 yield load prediction accuracy: FEA ensemble vs. experimental N=11 across two laboratories"
    }
  ],
  "wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4044760",
